<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>NOIR CLUB</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
}

html{
scroll-behavior:smooth;
}

body{
background:#0d0d0d;
color:white;
overflow-x:hidden;
}

header{
position:fixed;
top:0;
left:0;
width:100%;
padding:30px 8%;
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
z-index:1000;
background:rgba(13,13,13,.7);
backdrop-filter:blur(15px);
}

.logo{
font-size:1.4rem;
font-weight:900;
letter-spacing:4px;
}

.logo span{
color:#c6a972;
}

nav{
display:flex;
gap:35px;
}

nav a{
color:white;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:500;
opacity:.8;
transition:.3s;
}

nav a:hover{
opacity:1;
color:#c6a972;
}

.hero{
height:100vh;
background:
linear-gradient(
to right,
rgba(0,0,0,.9),
rgba(0,0,0,.45)
),
url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542751371-adc38448a05e?w=2200");
background-size:cover;
background-position:center;
display:flex;
align-items:center;
padding:0 8%;
}

.hero-content{
max-width:700px;
}

.hero h1{
font-size:6rem;
line-height:.95;
font-weight:900;
margin-bottom:30px;
}

.hero p{
font-size:1.2rem;
line-height:2;
color:#d0d0d0;
max-width:550px;
}

.btn{
display:inline-block;
margin-top:35px;
padding:18px 42px;
background:#c6a972;
color:black;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:700;
border-radius:999px;
transition:.3s;
}

.btn:hover{
transform:translateY(-4px);
}

section{
padding:120px 8%;
}

.title{
font-size:3rem;
font-weight:900;
margin-bottom:25px;
}

.subtitle{
color:#bdbdbd;
line-height:2;
max-width:700px;
}

.about{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
gap:60px;
align-items:center;
}

.about img{
width:100%;
height:650px;
object-fit:cover;
border-radius:30px;
}

.features{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
gap:30px;
margin-top:60px;
}

.card{
background:#151515;
padding:40px;
border-radius:30px;
border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
transition:.4s;
}

.card:hover{
transform:translateY(-10px);
border-color:#c6a972;
}

.card h3{
font-size:1.4rem;
margin-bottom:15px;
}

.card p{
color:#a7a7a7;
line-height:1.8;
}

.gallery{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);
gap:30px;
}

.gallery img{
width:100%;
height:500px;
object-fit:cover;
border-radius:30px;
transition:.5s;
}

.gallery img:hover{
transform:scale(1.03);
}

.cta{
background:#151515;
border-radius:40px;
padding:90px;
text-align:center;
}

.cta h2{
font-size:4rem;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.cta p{
max-width:700px;
margin:auto;
line-height:2;
color:#c5c5c5;
}

footer{
padding:40px;
text-align:center;
color:#999;
border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);
}

.reveal{
opacity:0;
transform:translateY(60px);
transition:1s;
}

.reveal.active{
opacity:1;
transform:translateY(0);
}

@media(max-width:1000px){

.about{
grid-template-columns:1fr;
}

.features{
grid-template-columns:1fr;
}

.gallery{
grid-template-columns:1fr;
}

.hero h1{
font-size:3.5rem;
}

nav{
display:none;
}

.cta h2{
font-size:2.3rem;
}
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>

<div class="logo">
NOIR<span>.</span>
</div>

<nav>
<a href="#">Início</a>
<a href="#">Espaço</a>
<a href="#">Experiência</a>
<a href="#">Contato</a>
</nav>

</header>

<section class="hero">

<div class="hero-content">

<h1>
A NOVA ERA
DO DIGITAL
</h1>

<p>
Mais do que uma lan house.
Um ambiente premium para jogar,
criar, trabalhar e viver experiências
de alto nível.
</p>

<a href="#" class="btn">
Reservar Agora
</a>

</div>

</section>

<section class="reveal">

<div class="about">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511512578047-dfb367046420?w=1800">

<div>

<h2 class="title">
Exclusividade em cada detalhe
</h2>

<p class="subtitle">
Projetado para oferecer conforto,
performance e sofisticação.
Equipamentos de última geração,
ambiente climatizado e estrutura
pensada para quem busca excelência.
</p>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="reveal">

<h2 class="title">
Uma experiência diferente
</h2>

<div class="features">

<div class="card">
<h3>Performance</h3>
<p>
Máquinas de alto desempenho para qualquer atividade.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Conforto</h3>
<p>
Ambientes silenciosos e preparados para longas sessões.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Exclusividade</h3>
<p>
Um espaço premium para clientes exigentes.
</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="reveal">

<h2 class="title">
Ambiente
</h2>

<div class="gallery">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542751371-adc38448a05e?w=1800">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1593305841991-05c297ba4575?w=1800">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511512578047-dfb367046420?w=1800">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542751110-97427bbecf20?w=1800">

</div>

</section>

<section class="reveal">

<div class="cta">

<h2>
Pronto para conhecer o futuro?
</h2>

<p>
Reserve sua estação e descubra uma nova forma de viver tecnologia e entretenimento.
</p>

<a href="#" class="btn">
Entrar para o Clube
</a>

</div>

</section>

<footer>
© 2026 NOIR CLUB • Todos os direitos reservados
</footer>

<script>

const reveals = document.querySelectorAll('.reveal');

window.addEventListener('scroll',()=>{

reveals.forEach(item=>{

const top = item.getBoundingClientRect().top;

if(top < window.innerHeight - 100){
item.classList.add('active');
}

});

});

</script>

</body>
</html>
